[
  {
    "text": "Best holiday ever. Happy birthday to",
    "start": 0.56,
    "duration": 6.64
  },
  {
    "text": "you.",
    "start": 4.48,
    "duration": 4.88
  },
  {
    "text": "What is that?",
    "start": 7.2,
    "duration": 4.64
  },
  {
    "text": "Mayday. Mayday. Mayday. Mayday. This is",
    "start": 9.36,
    "duration": 5.48
  },
  {
    "text": "the",
    "start": 11.84,
    "duration": 3.0
  },
  {
    "text": "Ben.",
    "start": 16.96,
    "duration": 3.0
  },
  {
    "text": "Dad, where's the scene?",
    "start": 20.24,
    "duration": 6.32
  },
  {
    "text": "This is enough. Captain of the Shankai.",
    "start": 24.0,
    "duration": 4.88
  },
  {
    "text": "So happy to finally hear someone. Do you",
    "start": 26.56,
    "duration": 4.16
  },
  {
    "text": "have any idea what happened? Revers over",
    "start": 28.88,
    "duration": 5.359
  },
  {
    "text": "the magnetic poles. The ocean retreated",
    "start": 30.72,
    "duration": 5.999
  },
  {
    "text": "and submerged the mainlands.",
    "start": 34.239,
    "duration": 4.561
  },
  {
    "text": "According to your coordinates, you're 2",
    "start": 36.719,
    "duration": 4.241
  },
  {
    "text": "or 3 days away. We have a good chance of",
    "start": 38.8,
    "duration": 6.919
  },
  {
    "text": "making it before the ocean comes back.",
    "start": 40.96,
    "duration": 4.759
  },
  {
    "text": "We got attacked by something.",
    "start": 47.92,
    "duration": 7.279
  },
  {
    "text": "What is this? Aropost from the abyss.",
    "start": 51.36,
    "duration": 7.44
  },
  {
    "text": "The oxygen seems to drive them crazy.",
    "start": 55.199,
    "duration": 6.081
  },
  {
    "text": "You need to hurry. Dusty is coming back",
    "start": 58.8,
    "duration": 6.2
  },
  {
    "text": "faster than I expected.",
    "start": 61.28,
    "duration": 3.72
  },
  {
    "text": "This is going to be really violent.",
    "start": 65.439,
    "duration": 4.441
  },
  {
    "text": "coming fan of heroes, but even I can't",
    "start": 86.36,
    "duration": 6.16
  },
  {
    "text": "deny the good that you've",
    "start": 90.159,
    "duration": 6.081
  },
  {
    "text": "done. Work with me, Sam. Country needs",
    "start": 92.52,
    "duration": 7.12
  },
  {
    "text": "Captain America.",
    "start": 96.24,
    "duration": 3.4
  },
  {
    "text": "The world is on the brink of",
    "start": 100.799,
    "duration": 8.96
  },
  {
    "text": "war. It's my job to fix",
    "start": 104.04,
    "duration": 5.719
  },
  {
    "text": "it. What if it's a trap? Stand by for",
    "start": 111.159,
    "duration": 5.24
  },
  {
    "text": "proof of",
    "start": 114.0,
    "duration": 2.399
  },
  {
    "text": "that. Somebody who's pulling the strings",
    "start": 116.52,
    "duration": 4.48
  },
  {
    "text": "on",
    "start": 119.52,
    "duration": 4.239
  },
  {
    "text": "everything. Captain America. You don't",
    "start": 121.0,
    "duration": 6.64
  },
  {
    "text": "even know what this is.",
    "start": 123.759,
    "duration": 3.881
  },
  {
    "text": "You want me? Come and get me.",
    "start": 128.8,
    "duration": 4.599
  },
  {
    "text": "[Music]",
    "start": 137.64,
    "duration": 7.52
  },
  {
    "text": "The world is changing.",
    "start": 141.04,
    "duration": 4.12
  },
  {
    "text": "[Music]",
    "start": 146.41,
    "duration": 3.11
  },
  {
    "text": "Who knows how deep the shadow's roots",
    "start": 148.0,
    "duration": 4.5
  },
  {
    "text": "have taken hold here. We",
    "start": 149.52,
    "duration": 6.64
  },
  {
    "text": "[Music]",
    "start": 152.5,
    "duration": 7.42
  },
  {
    "text": "I have seen a thousand thousand",
    "start": 156.16,
    "duration": 3.76
  },
  {
    "text": "futures. In every future where I",
    "start": 163.56,
    "duration": 5.28
  },
  {
    "text": "[Music]",
    "start": 166.81,
    "duration": 4.99
  },
  {
    "text": "lived, Ran",
    "start": 168.84,
    "duration": 7.08
  },
  {
    "text": "dies. And the only way he",
    "start": 171.8,
    "duration": 4.12
  },
  {
    "text": "lives is if I",
    "start": 177.72,
    "duration": 3.64
  },
  {
    "text": "[Music]",
    "start": 187.71,
    "duration": 3.859
  },
  {
    "text": "don't afford to fail again",
    "start": 195.0,
    "duration": 4.72
  },
  {
    "text": "in",
    "start": 201.92,
    "duration": 4.599
  },
  {
    "text": "2120 Mother",
    "start": 203.879,
    "duration": 6.961
  },
  {
    "text": "Earth is expecting",
    "start": 206.519,
    "duration": 4.321
  },
  {
    "text": "[Music]",
    "start": 212.31,
    "duration": 16.029
  },
  {
    "text": "[Music]",
    "start": 234.84,
    "duration": 3.129
  },
  {
    "text": "I hope someone finds",
    "start": 242.64,
    "duration": 5.159
  },
  {
    "text": "this. The event wasn't just one",
    "start": 244.92,
    "duration": 6.76
  },
  {
    "text": "thing. It was a slow creep.",
    "start": 247.799,
    "duration": 6.44
  },
  {
    "text": "No one said or did anything to stop",
    "start": 251.68,
    "duration": 5.559
  },
  {
    "text": "them.",
    "start": 254.239,
    "duration": 3.0
  },
  {
    "text": "It's our memory they want to wipe",
    "start": 259.12,
    "duration": 3.679
  },
  {
    "text": "out. This year, 72% of the world is",
    "start": 265.24,
    "duration": 7.0
  },
  {
    "text": "under authoritarian rule. We're now in a",
    "start": 268.88,
    "duration": 6.08
  },
  {
    "text": "democratic recession and it's endemic in",
    "start": 272.24,
    "duration": 5.6
  },
  {
    "text": "Europe, in the United States, India, the",
    "start": 274.96,
    "duration": 6.16
  },
  {
    "text": "Philippines. Minorities silenced,",
    "start": 277.84,
    "duration": 6.24
  },
  {
    "text": "dissenters arrested, social media",
    "start": 281.12,
    "duration": 4.799
  },
  {
    "text": "cooperative.",
    "start": 284.08,
    "duration": 3.92
  },
  {
    "text": "We are worth more when we are addicted,",
    "start": 285.919,
    "duration": 4.72
  },
  {
    "text": "polarized, and disinformed than if we",
    "start": 288.0,
    "duration": 7.24
  },
  {
    "text": "are living, breathing free citizens.",
    "start": 290.639,
    "duration": 4.601
  },
  {
    "text": "Where in New San Francisco have you",
    "start": 298.08,
    "duration": 5.08
  },
  {
    "text": "visited?",
    "start": 300.16,
    "duration": 3.0
  },
  {
    "text": "If you don't have facts, you can't have",
    "start": 304.639,
    "duration": 4.56
  },
  {
    "text": "truth. Without truth, you can't have",
    "start": 306.72,
    "duration": 5.479
  },
  {
    "text": "trust.",
    "start": 309.199,
    "duration": 3.0
  },
  {
    "text": "We have faced wars and famines and",
    "start": 313.12,
    "duration": 4.079
  },
  {
    "text": "genocides, but this is bigger than any",
    "start": 315.039,
    "duration": 4.321
  },
  {
    "text": "of",
    "start": 317.199,
    "duration": 2.161
  },
  {
    "text": "that. It's too late for me. May not be",
    "start": 326.36,
    "duration": 6.96
  },
  {
    "text": "too late for you.",
    "start": 329.759,
    "duration": 3.561
  },
  {
    "text": "I found something buried in the woods.",
    "start": 336.4,
    "duration": 4.799
  },
  {
    "text": "Dad, this is unacceptable. Do you",
    "start": 339.039,
    "duration": 5.16
  },
  {
    "text": "understand?",
    "start": 341.199,
    "duration": 3.0
  },
  {
    "text": "Come on, kid. Pay up. Whoa. Where'd you",
    "start": 350.16,
    "duration": 7.56
  },
  {
    "text": "two find an old Republic credit?",
    "start": 353.199,
    "duration": 4.521
  },
  {
    "text": "Over here. Quick. I'll get you home.",
    "start": 358.16,
    "duration": 4.56
  },
  {
    "text": "We'll make a partnership. We have to",
    "start": 360.72,
    "duration": 5.319
  },
  {
    "text": "move fast.",
    "start": 362.72,
    "duration": 3.319
  },
  {
    "text": "I need you to take the controls.",
    "start": 366.479,
    "duration": 6.28
  },
  {
    "text": "Okay. Neil.",
    "start": 369.52,
    "duration": 8.08
  },
  {
    "text": "Neil, please don't give up. No matter",
    "start": 372.759,
    "duration": 7.841
  },
  {
    "text": "what.",
    "start": 377.6,
    "duration": 3.0
  },
  {
    "text": "Are you ready?",
    "start": 381.44,
    "duration": 5.56
  },
  {
    "text": "Yeah.",
    "start": 384.0,
    "duration": 3.0
  },
  {
    "text": "[Music]",
    "start": 388.41,
    "duration": 3.109
  },
  {
    "text": "What do you remember?",
    "start": 392.639,
    "duration": 3.441
  },
  {
    "text": "Remember just",
    "start": 401.24,
    "duration": 3.72
  },
  {
    "text": "moments",
    "start": 407.72,
    "duration": 3.0
  },
  {
    "text": "images when I woke up. There is no one",
    "start": 412.199,
    "duration": 6.401
  },
  {
    "text": "left. No one left.",
    "start": 414.88,
    "duration": 3.72
  },
  {
    "text": "[Music]",
    "start": 422.88,
    "duration": 3.67
  },
  {
    "text": "What happened here? What happened here?",
    "start": 426.88,
    "duration": 4.439
  },
  {
    "text": "We live in a world where nothing can be",
    "start": 444.479,
    "duration": 6.0
  },
  {
    "text": "taken for granted. Not even the air we",
    "start": 447.44,
    "duration": 5.759
  },
  {
    "text": "breathe. Protect yourselves. Take your",
    "start": 450.479,
    "duration": 6.0
  },
  {
    "text": "air. That's you. You buy.",
    "start": 453.199,
    "duration": 4.961
  },
  {
    "text": "Yeah, but it's not like I'm saving the",
    "start": 456.479,
    "duration": 3.84
  },
  {
    "text": "world or anything. They just liked my",
    "start": 458.16,
    "duration": 5.52
  },
  {
    "text": "look. Air remedy has become the most",
    "start": 460.319,
    "duration": 6.641
  },
  {
    "text": "sought after drug in the world.",
    "start": 463.68,
    "duration": 6.32
  },
  {
    "text": "It completely neutralizes the toxin. Air",
    "start": 466.96,
    "duration": 6.16
  },
  {
    "text": "will be available to everyone.",
    "start": 470.0,
    "duration": 4.879
  },
  {
    "text": "There goes the planet. We're all going",
    "start": 473.12,
    "duration": 4.16
  },
  {
    "text": "to be slaves to there. Not if I can help",
    "start": 474.879,
    "duration": 5.401
  },
  {
    "text": "it.",
    "start": 477.28,
    "duration": 3.0
  },
  {
    "text": "I don't know what's happening.",
    "start": 485.199,
    "duration": 3.72
  },
  {
    "text": "Tell me about this drug. It's done.",
    "start": 493.759,
    "duration": 4.081
  },
  {
    "text": "things to me.",
    "start": 495.68,
    "duration": 3.68
  },
  {
    "text": "Whatever we're looking at, it's not",
    "start": 497.84,
    "duration": 4.0
  },
  {
    "text": "human.",
    "start": 499.36,
    "duration": 4.88
  },
  {
    "text": "Remarkable. We could create a whole new",
    "start": 501.84,
    "duration": 5.199
  },
  {
    "text": "population to harvest.",
    "start": 504.24,
    "duration": 6.48
  },
  {
    "text": "In addition to harvesting her,",
    "start": 507.039,
    "duration": 6.721
  },
  {
    "text": "out of time. Ether wants to be the only",
    "start": 510.72,
    "duration": 6.239
  },
  {
    "text": "solution, but it isn't.",
    "start": 513.76,
    "duration": 5.519
  },
  {
    "text": "You think it's okay to experiment on",
    "start": 516.959,
    "duration": 5.281
  },
  {
    "text": "people?",
    "start": 519.279,
    "duration": 4.64
  },
  {
    "text": "What's more important? Your future or",
    "start": 522.24,
    "duration": 5.4
  },
  {
    "text": "the future of the species.",
    "start": 523.919,
    "duration": 3.721
  },
  {
    "text": "You don't get the blade gone.",
    "start": 529.04,
    "duration": 6.08
  },
  {
    "text": "I am not giving you the formula. We'll",
    "start": 532.56,
    "duration": 5.6
  },
  {
    "text": "let people die.",
    "start": 535.12,
    "duration": 5.04
  },
  {
    "text": "Look what it's done to me. It's just",
    "start": 538.16,
    "duration": 6.239
  },
  {
    "text": "side effects. Just side",
    "start": 540.16,
    "duration": 4.239
  },
  {
    "text": "effects.",
    "start": 545.72,
    "duration": 3.0
  },
  {
    "text": "[Music]",
    "start": 551.12,
    "duration": 8.12
  },
  {
    "text": "Either we change or we die.",
    "start": 553.64,
    "duration": 5.6
  },
  {
    "text": "All right, guys. Hey, Dad. Hey, Dad. I",
    "start": 561.76,
    "duration": 5.199
  },
  {
    "text": "want you to have a really fun and also",
    "start": 564.0,
    "duration": 5.44
  },
  {
    "text": "safe somewhere out here. I only have one",
    "start": 566.959,
    "duration": 5.681
  },
  {
    "text": "rule. Stay out of the basement.",
    "start": 569.44,
    "duration": 6.16
  },
  {
    "text": "What do you got in the basement?",
    "start": 572.64,
    "duration": 5.44
  },
  {
    "text": "Did you guys know that Devon and Cece's",
    "start": 575.6,
    "duration": 4.0
  },
  {
    "text": "uncle was one of the kids that went",
    "start": 578.08,
    "duration": 3.759
  },
  {
    "text": "missing in 1994?",
    "start": 579.6,
    "duration": 5.2
  },
  {
    "text": "I can't get you out of my He finally",
    "start": 581.839,
    "duration": 5.041
  },
  {
    "text": "processed your quest. Only took you 30",
    "start": 584.8,
    "duration": 3.68
  },
  {
    "text": "years. What is that? My brother's",
    "start": 586.88,
    "duration": 5.639
  },
  {
    "text": "clothes from the night he died.",
    "start": 588.48,
    "duration": 4.039
  },
  {
    "text": "They were killed by ghost. No, nobody",
    "start": 592.88,
    "duration": 7.32
  },
  {
    "text": "knows what happened. Yo, check this out.",
    "start": 595.44,
    "duration": 4.76
  },
  {
    "text": "What the hell is this?",
    "start": 603.279,
    "duration": 4.12
  },
  {
    "text": "Dad, not a good time, dumbass.",
    "start": 609.88,
    "duration": 7.36
  },
  {
    "text": "Holy crap, there's something in my",
    "start": 614.24,
    "duration": 5.159
  },
  {
    "text": "[Music]",
    "start": 617.24,
    "duration": 5.719
  },
  {
    "text": "arm. Hey, um, what kind of plant should",
    "start": 619.399,
    "duration": 8.961
  },
  {
    "text": "you always watch out for? Uh, an ambush.",
    "start": 622.959,
    "duration": 5.401
  },
  {
    "text": "What's going on with that? I don't know.",
    "start": 630.079,
    "duration": 3.2
  },
  {
    "text": "Trey, your car. It's in my driveway",
    "start": 631.6,
    "duration": 3.52
  },
  {
    "text": "again. Trespassing. Yo, what are you",
    "start": 633.279,
    "duration": 4.24
  },
  {
    "text": "doing? Are you out of your mind? It's a",
    "start": 635.12,
    "duration": 5.8
  },
  {
    "text": "distinct possibility.",
    "start": 637.519,
    "duration": 3.401
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh, that's not good.",
    "start": 644.64,
    "duration": 3.8
  },
  {
    "text": "Things have been happening that are not",
    "start": 649.36,
    "duration": 3.68
  },
  {
    "text": "normal.",
    "start": 651.04,
    "duration": 4.479
  },
  {
    "text": "Trey's missing. That kid's missing.",
    "start": 653.04,
    "duration": 5.799
  },
  {
    "text": "Sound familiar?",
    "start": 655.519,
    "duration": 3.32
  },
  {
    "text": "Dodge behind all the crazy stuff",
    "start": 659.68,
    "duration": 2.96
  },
  {
    "text": "happening. We don't know for sure that",
    "start": 661.279,
    "duration": 3.601
  },
  {
    "text": "he",
    "start": 662.64,
    "duration": 2.24
  },
  {
    "text": "is not controlling a car. I don't know",
    "start": 665.8,
    "duration": 6.84
  },
  {
    "text": "if I want to be down here.",
    "start": 669.519,
    "duration": 4.481
  },
  {
    "text": "You don't have a kid in your basement,",
    "start": 672.64,
    "duration": 4.439
  },
  {
    "text": "do you? No. That would",
    "start": 674.0,
    "duration": 6.88
  },
  {
    "text": "be No.",
    "start": 677.079,
    "duration": 6.341
  },
  {
    "text": "Are you okay?",
    "start": 680.88,
    "duration": 5.65
  },
  {
    "text": "[Music]",
    "start": 683.42,
    "duration": 3.11
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh no. I made you",
    "start": 686.959,
    "duration": 4.12
  },
  {
    "text": "and I unmake you.",
    "start": 692.64,
    "duration": 9.129
  },
  {
    "text": "[Music]",
    "start": 695.08,
    "duration": 6.689
  },
  {
    "text": "There is so much this world can teach",
    "start": 702.64,
    "duration": 5.56
  },
  {
    "text": "us.",
    "start": 705.2,
    "duration": 3.0
  },
  {
    "text": "Joe, if you're seeing",
    "start": 715.0,
    "duration": 2.04
  },
  {
    "text": "[Music]",
    "start": 716.86,
    "duration": 1.34
  },
  {
    "text": "[Applause]",
    "start": 717.04,
    "duration": 6.039
  },
  {
    "text": "this, something's happened to me.",
    "start": 718.2,
    "duration": 4.879
  },
  {
    "text": "I need your help.",
    "start": 725.519,
    "duration": 5.76
  },
  {
    "text": "What is happening?",
    "start": 728.639,
    "duration": 6.961
  },
  {
    "text": "I saw you die. I saw someone kill you.",
    "start": 731.279,
    "duration": 5.641
  },
  {
    "text": "There's",
    "start": 735.6,
    "duration": 6.919
  },
  {
    "text": "technology. the first digital universe.",
    "start": 736.92,
    "duration": 5.599
  },
  {
    "text": "I found a way in.",
    "start": 743.36,
    "duration": 3.719
  },
  {
    "text": "Track him.",
    "start": 747.36,
    "duration": 10.12
  },
  {
    "text": "I'm fixing it. Now they're after you.",
    "start": 750.32,
    "duration": 7.16
  },
  {
    "text": "So what does that make me?",
    "start": 757.6,
    "duration": 6.56
  },
  {
    "text": "This is as real as anything I know.",
    "start": 760.639,
    "duration": 6.64
  },
  {
    "text": "We're risking exposure.",
    "start": 764.16,
    "duration": 4.479
  },
  {
    "text": "becomes like a switch and you are gone",
    "start": 767.279,
    "duration": 5.0
  },
  {
    "text": "like you never existed.",
    "start": 768.639,
    "duration": 3.64
  },
  {
    "text": "It's time for a",
    "start": 772.88,
    "duration": 2.72
  },
  {
    "text": "reboot. Is this real?",
    "start": 779.0,
    "duration": 4.399
  },
  {
    "text": "What's the big question? What if",
    "start": 785.04,
    "duration": 4.919
  },
  {
    "text": "everything you know to be",
    "start": 787.6,
    "duration": 7.799
  },
  {
    "text": "true was just one big lie?",
    "start": 789.959,
    "duration": 5.44
  },
  {
    "text": "For as long as we can",
    "start": 801.04,
    "duration": 5.56
  },
  {
    "text": "remember, everyone that goes",
    "start": 803.16,
    "duration": 6.359
  },
  {
    "text": "outside, if killed by the dangerous",
    "start": 806.6,
    "duration": 7.28
  },
  {
    "text": "toxins of an unsafe world,",
    "start": 809.519,
    "duration": 4.361
  },
  {
    "text": "Juliet Nicholls asked to go",
    "start": 814.079,
    "duration": 6.88
  },
  {
    "text": "out. She was a fighter.",
    "start": 816.36,
    "duration": 8.599
  },
  {
    "text": "Warning, oxygen levels low.",
    "start": 820.959,
    "duration": 5.081
  },
  {
    "text": "But she",
    "start": 824.959,
    "duration": 9.0
  },
  {
    "text": "died. A hero to the silo. They're lying.",
    "start": 826.04,
    "duration": 7.919
  },
  {
    "text": "She might be out there somewhere, still",
    "start": 834.8,
    "duration": 6.039
  },
  {
    "text": "alive.",
    "start": 837.839,
    "duration": 3.0
  },
  {
    "text": "[Applause]",
    "start": 841.66,
    "duration": 4.58
  },
  {
    "text": "The lies have to stop. People are saying",
    "start": 842.88,
    "duration": 7.079
  },
  {
    "text": "it's time for a rebellion.",
    "start": 846.24,
    "duration": 3.719
  },
  {
    "text": "You can't control what he means to",
    "start": 851.36,
    "duration": 4.68
  },
  {
    "text": "people.",
    "start": 853.04,
    "duration": 3.0
  },
  {
    "text": "I need to know what happened here.",
    "start": 856.639,
    "duration": 6.44
  },
  {
    "text": "For my friends, my",
    "start": 860.8,
    "duration": 5.0
  },
  {
    "text": "family. All we're trying to do is",
    "start": 863.079,
    "duration": 7.161
  },
  {
    "text": "survive. Nothing's going to stop me from",
    "start": 865.8,
    "duration": 4.44
  },
  {
    "text": "trying. No.",
    "start": 870.6,
    "duration": 11.08
  },
  {
    "text": "[Music]",
    "start": 874.16,
    "duration": 10.08
  },
  {
    "text": "You're frightened. I'm not afraid of the",
    "start": 881.68,
    "duration": 4.3
  },
  {
    "text": "rebellion.",
    "start": 884.24,
    "duration": 4.48
  },
  {
    "text": "[Music]",
    "start": 885.98,
    "duration": 4.219
  },
  {
    "text": "I'm more",
    "start": 888.72,
    "duration": 5.2
  },
  {
    "text": "afraid of what she",
    "start": 890.199,
    "duration": 3.721
  },
  {
    "text": "saw. So many things we were",
    "start": 896.68,
    "duration": 4.279
  },
  {
    "text": "seeing that no one has ever seen.",
    "start": 901.079,
    "duration": 5.32
  },
  {
    "text": "The corporations more powerful than any",
    "start": 909.04,
    "duration": 5.84
  },
  {
    "text": "country. We must maintain dominance.",
    "start": 911.88,
    "duration": 7.399
  },
  {
    "text": "That is why the Nautilus was developed.",
    "start": 914.88,
    "duration": 7.6
  },
  {
    "text": "I can taste freedom. Nemo. It's now or",
    "start": 919.279,
    "duration": 6.201
  },
  {
    "text": "never.",
    "start": 922.48,
    "duration": 3.0
  },
  {
    "text": "This is Nemo. We are taking control of",
    "start": 926.16,
    "duration": 4.96
  },
  {
    "text": "the Nautilus. We'll use it to escape.",
    "start": 928.079,
    "duration": 6.44
  },
  {
    "text": "Start the engine.",
    "start": 931.12,
    "duration": 3.399
  },
  {
    "text": "a submersible ship.",
    "start": 942.0,
    "duration": 4.279
  },
  {
    "text": "She is mine. I want her back. If you're",
    "start": 946.639,
    "duration": 4.481
  },
  {
    "text": "looking for someone to bring Nemo back",
    "start": 949.36,
    "duration": 4.32
  },
  {
    "text": "in chase, I'm your man. I'm going to",
    "start": 951.12,
    "duration": 3.839
  },
  {
    "text": "burn the whole damn company to the",
    "start": 953.68,
    "duration": 3.839
  },
  {
    "text": "ground.",
    "start": 954.959,
    "duration": 4.721
  },
  {
    "text": "My name is Humility Lucas. This man is",
    "start": 957.519,
    "duration": 3.601
  },
  {
    "text": "holding me against my will. When will I",
    "start": 959.68,
    "duration": 3.04
  },
  {
    "text": "be free? If I had any choice in the",
    "start": 961.12,
    "duration": 3.76
  },
  {
    "text": "matter, I would never see Isaac again.",
    "start": 962.72,
    "duration": 5.799
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh, utterly charming.",
    "start": 964.88,
    "duration": 3.639
  },
  {
    "text": "This Nemo, what did you make of him? He",
    "start": 968.56,
    "duration": 6.32
  },
  {
    "text": "is a convict. He is a pirate, stubborn,",
    "start": 972.24,
    "duration": 4.959
  },
  {
    "text": "brave, angry.",
    "start": 974.88,
    "duration": 4.16
  },
  {
    "text": "Whatever else this Nemo is, he'll be",
    "start": 977.199,
    "duration": 3.681
  },
  {
    "text": "dead soon.",
    "start": 979.04,
    "duration": 2.76
  },
  {
    "text": "Tell",
    "start": 980.88,
    "duration": 4.639
  },
  {
    "text": "me where are they headed? The Northeast",
    "start": 981.8,
    "duration": 5.08
  },
  {
    "text": "Passage. There are treasures there",
    "start": 985.519,
    "duration": 5.081
  },
  {
    "text": "beyond the man's imagination.",
    "start": 986.88,
    "duration": 3.72
  },
  {
    "text": "I have come a long way to rescue you.",
    "start": 991.839,
    "duration": 3.841
  },
  {
    "text": "Did it ever occur to you that I don't",
    "start": 994.32,
    "duration": 3.32
  },
  {
    "text": "need to be rescued? No.",
    "start": 995.68,
    "duration": 3.92
  },
  {
    "text": "[Music]",
    "start": 997.64,
    "duration": 3.96
  },
  {
    "text": "I'll see your hunt until the ends of the",
    "start": 999.6,
    "duration": 5.599
  },
  {
    "text": "earth. You'll be hunting in the wrong",
    "start": 1001.6,
    "duration": 3.599
  },
  {
    "text": "place. Doesn't matter if you chose to be",
    "start": 1013.079,
    "duration": 5.601
  },
  {
    "text": "here or not.",
    "start": 1015.279,
    "duration": 3.401
  },
  {
    "text": "All that matters is that we are each",
    "start": 1020.399,
    "duration": 5.081
  },
  {
    "text": "other's best hope.",
    "start": 1021.92,
    "duration": 3.56
  },
  {
    "text": "This is going to be such fun.",
    "start": 1026.559,
    "duration": 4.681
  },
  {
    "text": "But that person who did those",
    "start": 1032.88,
    "duration": 3.919
  },
  {
    "text": "things, that's still",
    "start": 1038.919,
    "duration": 5.681
  },
  {
    "text": "me now. That's who I",
    "start": 1041.4,
    "duration": 8.039
  },
  {
    "text": "fight every hour of every",
    "start": 1044.6,
    "duration": 4.839
  },
  {
    "text": "day. I don't always",
    "start": 1050.919,
    "duration": 8.521
  },
  {
    "text": "win to discover what you're capable",
    "start": 1053.64,
    "duration": 5.8
  },
  {
    "text": "of just for you.",
    "start": 1059.64,
    "duration": 5.52
  }
]